Caption The Wall That Heals STEPHEN DUNN / Hartford Courant The Wall That Heals, a half-scale replica of the Vietnam Veterans Memorial in Washington, D.C., arrived by truck, (right rear) in Manchester Wednesday accompanied by more that 200 motorcycle riders.

(STEPHEN DUNN / Hartford Courant) See The Wall That Heals STEPHEN DUNN / Hartford Courant The Wall That Heals, a half-scale replica of the Vietnam Veterans Memorial in Washington, D.C., arrived by truck in Manchester Wednesday accompanied by more that 200 motorcycle riders. The monument proceeded up Main Street and under a huge American flag to Center Memorial Park, where it is to be assembled and displayed through Sunday, Oct. 11.
